OL,3,CFears for the future of community
OL,4,Chospitals in the Scottish Borders
OL,6,FHundreds of people have signed a
OL,7,Fpetition amid fears that beds could
OL,8,Fclose at four community hospitals in
OL,9,Fthe due to a lack of medical cover..
OL,11,FThere are 92 community hospital beds
OL,12,Facross four sites in Kelso, Duns,
OL,13,FHawick and Peebles.
OL,15,FA Health and Social Care Partnership
OL,16,Freview was launched after GP cover
OL,17,Ffinished at a small hospital in Kelso
OL,18,Fand medical contracts ended at the
OL,19,FKnoll Hospital in Duns.
