OL,3,CFears for the future of community
OL,4,Chospitals in the Scottish Borders
OL,6,Fdoctors and nurse practitioners have
OL,7,Fso far filled the void, but the
OL,8,Ftemporary agreement is due to run out
OL,9,Fin August.
OL,11,FAgreements have been in place with
OL,12,Fnearby GP practices to provide medical
OL,13,Fcover for patients.
OL,15,FBut GPs in Kelso withdrew from the
OL,16,Farrangement in April due to an
OL,17,Fincreased workload within their own
OL,18,Fsurgeries.
OL,20,FAt the same time contracted medical
OL,21,Fcover in Duns came to an end.
