OL,3,CFears for the future of community
OL,4,Chospitals in the Scottish Borders
OL,6,FIt is feared that similar withdrawals
OL,7,Fcould happen in Peebles and Hawick due
OL,8,Fto current GP workloads.
OL,10,FRalph Roberts, NHS Borders chief
OL,11,Fexecutive, said the review would seek
OL,12,Fto ensure that medical cover at
OL,13,Fcommunity hospitals was "sustainable".
OL,15,FHe said: "Scottish Borders Health and
OL,16,FSocial Care Partnership is reviewing
OL,17,Fservices provided from our four
OL,18,Fcommunity hospitals to ensure they are
OL,19,Ffit for the future.
