OL,3,CFears for the future of community
OL,4,Chospitals in the Scottish Borders
OL,6,F"This will consider the changing needs
OL,7,Fof our population and the way in which
OL,8,Fhealth and social care should be
OL,9,Fprovided to best meet these needs.
OL,11,F"One element of the review is the
OL,12,Fprovision of medical cover in
OL,13,Fcommunity hospitals to ensure that it
OL,14,Fis sustainable.
