OL,3,CFears for the future of community
OL,4,Chospitals in the Scottish Borders
OL,6,F"The review will help us to redesign
OL,7,Four services to provide sustainable,
OL,8,Fhigh quality care for the long term
OL,9,Fand is being carried out openly and
OL,10,Ftransparently with the participation
OL,11,Fof our staff and communities and in
OL,12,Fline with the Health and Social Care
OL,13,FPartnership's Involving People
OL,14,FFramework.
OL,16,F"This process is in its very early
OL,17,Fstages and there are no plans at
OL,18,Fpresent to change community hospital
OL,19,Fprovision prior to the outcomes of the
OL,20,Freview."
