OL,4,Chospitals in the Scottish Borders
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the GPs at Teviot Medical
OL,7,FPractice in Hawick have issued a joint
OL,8,Fstatement reassuring the public that
OL,9,Fit is not their intention to withdraw
OL,10,Fcover from Hawick Community Hospital.
OL,12,FThe statement read: "The doctors at
OL,13,FTeviot Medical Practice have a long
OL,14,Fhistory of caring for patients at
OL,15,FHawick Community Hospital.
OL,17,F"We are keen to continue to provide
OL,18,Fsafe medical care for our inpatients.
